         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Wedderburn ¶ Decr 8th 1879 ¶ Dr Muiller ¶ Melbourne ¶ Dear Sir...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">79.12.08a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From Joshua Gray</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M1, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Zygophyllum</seg> (MEL 1517606). MS annotation by M: 'Answ 10/12/79 FvM'. Letter not found.</p>
               </note>Wedderburn<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Vic.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Decr 8th 1879</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dr Muiller</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I Enclose herewith a Sample of a weed which grows in many places in this district, Many Horses and Some horned Cattle have died soon after eating it and I therefore suspect it is poisonous I will receive it as a great favour if you will inform me of the name of the plant, If it is poisonous to horses and if so a likely <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Antidote</hi>
               </seg> for Same — and by so doing you will confer a very great favour on</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Your Obedient Servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>J. R. Gray</p>
         </div>
      </body>
